summary: @odd they’re great for the price. My fronts and surrounds are JAMOs. I have Polk in-ceiling speakers for the four “height” channels and a Polk Signature Elite ES35 for the center. I wish the center was beefier, but I’ll take the awesome projector over the center 😀
